beer.beer_description:
This beer will make you feel like Elvis, only alive.

Our take on the West Coast IPA: all your senses should be focused towards the truckload of hops we added to this beer (NZ and US varieties). Token hop aromas: citrus, pine, grapefruit. The hops overtake the palate with a lingering bitterness nearly as long as a Baywatch beach montage...
